<section class="py-32 bg-brand-snow">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Photo Column -->
      <div class="flex justify-center pt-16">
        <img 
          src="/alex-lee.jpeg" 
          alt="Alex Lee - Director & Founder"
          class="rounded-full w-64 h-64 object-cover object-top shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Bio Column -->
      <div>
        <span class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue font-bold mb-4 block">Meet Our Founder</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-text tracking-tight mb-6">Alex Lee</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-bold mb-4">Director & Founder</p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/80 font-normal leading-relaxed">
          Alex Lee is the Director & Founder of Alexis Employment Agency, bringing over a decade of diverse professional experience spanning the Republic of Singapore Navy, consumer sales, and corporate business development. His time in the Navy instilled in him a strong sense of discipline, integrity, and commitment to excellence, values that form the foundation of how Alexis Employment Agency operates today.
With hands-on experience serving consumers directly across multiple industries, Alex understands what people truly need: clear communication, genuine care, and reliable service. He founded Alexis Employment Agency to bring these same standards to domestic helper placement, ensuring every family receives a personalised, transparent, and trusted experience from start to finish.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
